## ğŸ§° Tools & Libraries

- [Analog Devices pyadi-iio](https://github.com/analogdevicesinc/pyadi-iio)  
- GNU Radio Companion (GRC)
- Python 3.8+
- NumPy, SciPy, matplotlib
- ADALM-PLUTO SDR (ADI AD9361)

